1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,262
=Episode 20=

17
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:09,560
Here's your coffee.

18
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,000
Welcome.

19
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,840
Who are you?

20
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,240
Sun.

21
00:01:40,525 --> 00:01:41,840
I'm your sister.

22
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,212
Why did they send me away?

23
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:06,240
Mom was suffering from
severe postpartum depression.

24
00:02:06,580 --> 00:02:09,280
Her intention in sending you away
was to let you leave the Lu family

25
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,600
and live a better life.

26
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,440
But we never expected

27
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,640
Grandpa and Grandma to keep using you

28
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,760
to demand money.

29
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,880
Then why me?

30
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,760
I wish it had been me instead.

31
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,640
But that wasn't something
we could decide.

32
00:02:35,712 --> 00:02:36,352
Sun,

33
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,160
now that I'm here,

34
00:02:39,337 --> 00:02:41,325
I won't let anyone hurt you again.

35
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:53,920
Sun,

36
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:57,240
I always knew I was going to die.

37
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,280
So I'm not afraid at all.

38
00:03:07,208 --> 00:03:09,040
I came too late,

39
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,760
and you suffered so much.

40
00:03:19,934 --> 00:03:21,280
Dad

41
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,480
isn't a bad person.

42
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,160
If you tell him

43
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,720
you're Lu Zhu,

44
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:36,320
you'll love you the way he loved me.

45
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,760
I'm giving your life

46
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,987
back to you.

47
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:48,360
From now on, live like bamboo.

48
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:53,320
Don't be Sun anymore.

49
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,360
Okay?

50
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,400
Zhu!

51
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,160
Zhu!

52
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,760
Wake up, Zhu!

53
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,440
Zhu...

54
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,800
Mr. Lu.

55
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,600
Have some fruit.

56
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,720
Thank you.

57
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,200
Man, you're so kind.

58
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:24,680
Mom.

59
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,960
Man,

60
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,200
I've always liked you

61
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,560
and appreciated your talent.

62
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,600
Don't worry.

63
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,360
There'll be a place for you
in the Lu Group.

64
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,400
But you must work hard.

65
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,800
Thank you for thinking highly of me.

66
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,480
Lu.

67
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:41,880
Come.

68
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:45,200
Don't do anything else recently.

69
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,400
Get ready with your things.

70
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:48,840
You'll go to Singapore
with Tianze to study

71
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:50,320
this autumn.

72
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,400
Alright.

73
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,360
This matter

74
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,160
ends here.

75
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,840
Since you two are siblings,

76
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,400
then behave like siblings.

77
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,160
Don't think about
anything inappropriate.

78
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,680
Man,

79
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:11,000
bring your fiancée home

80
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,760
for dinner sometime.

81
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,320
We're family. We should meet.

82
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,120
Zhu,

83
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:27,680
I hit you

84
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,760
and upset you.

85
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,560
All your life,

86
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,760
I've never laid a finger on you.

87
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,720
I'm sorry.

88
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,400
However,

89
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:40,760
shouldn't you also apologize
to someone?

90
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:50,880
Ms. Huang.

91
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,280
I'm sorry.

92
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:57,400
It's alright.

93
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,000
We're family.

94
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,600
You should call her mom.

95
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,560
Dad,

96
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,320
I can't.

97
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:19,040
Alright. Don't make things difficult for her.

98
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,280
I'm fine now.

99
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,120
It's over.

100
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,320
Man is engaged.

101
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,320
It's all in the past.

102
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:34,800
Come in.

103
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,240
Mr. Lu, I want to ask you something.

104
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,080
Go ahead.

105
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:56,600
The Lu Group has never been involved
in the medical industry.

106
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:57,840
Why did you suddenly

107
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,600
give Yihang an order worth 300 million?

108
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,160
Is there a problem?

109
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,600
I don't understand.

110
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,840
Man,

111
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,840
I've been waiting for you

112
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,760
to come and ask me.

113
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:14,520
Luckily, I was right about you.

114
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,840
You have integrity.

115
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,640
I know

116
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:21,240
why you were so determined
to join the Lu Group.

117
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,240
That's why I didn't stop you.

118
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,040
I even gave you a lot of authority.

119
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,080
I wanted you

120
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:29,280
to investigate this matter yourself.

121
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:36,880
Your father's

122
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,040
suicide

123
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,600
had nothing to do with anyone else.

124
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,160
I know my father.

125
00:08:44,025 --> 00:08:45,187
He wasn't that kind of person.

126
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:48,760
The company

127
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,200
keeps all original contract copies.

128
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:53,360
Back then, when your father came to me
seeking financing,

129
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,640
he said

130
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:58,600
he wanted to build
a pharmaceutical factory in India.

131
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:01,520
I rejected him very clearly.

132
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,760
But somehow, the financial world
spread rumors

133
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:05,760
that I had given him
a 300-million-yuan order.

134
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,040
So he easily secured

135
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:10,960
nearly ten billion in financing.

136
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,160
Do you understand?

137
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,320
He not only forged the contract,

138
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,920
but also our company's official seal.

139
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,520
When I obtained this evidence,

140
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,720
I was...

141
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,280
I was hesitating about

142
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:28,480
whether to sue him.

143
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,480
(Wanhe Group, Dingxin Group)
But before I could take any action,

144
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,320
he committed suicide.

145
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:37,680
Ye was bold and ambitious.

146
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,400
He built everything from scratch

147
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,240
and operated in both legitimate
and shady circles.

148
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,600
But he lacked discipline.

149
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,600
He went too far that time.

150
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,240
Those investment firms in Shenzhen

151
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,720
aren't easy to mess with.

152
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,560
They quickly uncovered the problem.

153
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:55,280
Your father knew that

154
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:56,880
if he didn't die, he would go to prison.

155
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,840
But I didn't expect him

156
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,440
to choose suicide.

157
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,200
It's a pity.

158
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,080
Man,

159
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:08,880
you're a good young man.

160
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:10,320
I've seen

161
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:13,440
that you're steady

162
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,440
and upright.

163
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,840
You're not like your father.

164
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:20,840
Oh.

165
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,520
Well.

166
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,120
Putting everything aside,

167
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,760
I value your ability.

168
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:27,440
I hope you'll stay with the Lu Group.

169
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:29,520
Previously,

170
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,520
Zhu asked me to give you a chance.

171
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,840
This is the official
employment contract.

172
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,120
Sign it,

173
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:38,320
and you'll become the youngest
vice chairman

174
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,760
at the Lu Group headquarters.

175
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,160
Mr. Lu,

176
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,480
thank you.

177
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,740
Thank you for telling me all this.

178
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,240
I'll give my father

179
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:04,960
an explanation.

180
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,320
(Turns out the truth
I've been searching for)

181
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,480
(was this.)

182
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:27,760
(The things I was so certain of)

183
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:28,960
(were all false.)

184
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,320
(Dad,)

185
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:34,080
(you were so foolish.)

186
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,480
After Mr. Ye came out
of Mr. Lu's office,

187
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,400
he's been like this.

188
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:43,880
I don't know what happened.

189
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,240
Man,

190
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,280
what's done is done.

191
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:57,920
Don't be too upset.

192
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,290
The company needs you.

193
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,280
I need you.

194
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:06,080
There's nothing left that needs me.

195
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,400
Man,

196
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:13,280
I don't know what exactly happened,

197
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,080
but...

198
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,480
Let's get engaged.

199
00:12:24,562 --> 00:12:29,062
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

200
00:12:29,287 --> 00:12:33,075
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

201
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:37,325
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

202
00:12:37,325 --> 00:12:41,462
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

203
00:12:41,587 --> 00:12:45,362
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

204
00:12:45,362 --> 00:12:49,137
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

205
00:12:49,137 --> 00:12:51,412
♪The you in my memories♪

206
00:12:51,412 --> 00:12:53,425
♪Will fade from clarity♪

207
00:12:53,425 --> 00:12:58,862
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

208
00:13:00,425 --> 00:13:05,862
♪Forget you completely?♪
